lead_paragraph: Stowers blew past a 100-meter hurdles field that included the 2012 Olympic gold medalist Dawn Harper-Nelson and Queen Harrison to win in a Drake Relays-record 12.40 seconds.

headline.main: Jasmin Stowers Wins Hurdles and Sets Record at Drake Relays

abstract: Jasmin Stowers wins 100-meter hurdles at Drake Relays in record 12.40 seconds.
